msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.6:17.6"
msgid "vigatamalamaccherena cetasā ajjhāgāraṃ vasati muttacāgo payatapāṇi vossaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato. "
msgstr "They live at home rid of the stain of stinginess, freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving to give and to share. "

msgctxt "sn55.6:17.7"
msgid "Imehi kho, thapatayo, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc18
msgctxt "sn55.6:18.1"
msgid "Tumhe kho, thapatayo, buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgatā—"
msgstr "And you have experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.2"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.3"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.4"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.5"
msgid "yaṃ kho pana kiñci kule deyyadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ appaṭivibhattaṃ sīlavantehi kalyāṇadhammehi. "
msgstr "And whatever there is in your family that’s available to give, you share it all with those who are ethical, of good character. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.6:18.6"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, thapatayo, "
msgstr "What do you think, chamberlains? "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.7"
msgid "katividhā te kosalesu manussā ye tumhākaṃ samasamā, yadidaṃ—"
msgstr "How many people among the Kosalans are your equal "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.8"
msgid "dānasaṃvibhāge”ti? "
msgstr "when it comes to giving and sharing?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.6:18.9"
msgid "“Lābhā no, bhante, suladdhaṃ no, bhante. "
msgstr "“We’re fortunate, sir, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn55.6:18.10"
msgid "Yesaṃ no bhagavā evaṃ pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "in that the Buddha understands us like this.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.6:18.11"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

